    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/600_150_B_Palallel.png?t=1655243984\" /></span><br><br>Discover a brand-new cooperative experience with <strong>Palallel</strong>, a 2D puzzle platformer for two players !<br> <br>Trapped in themed boards, find your way through the puzzles and get to the exit. But don’t forget your partner !<br><br>Each player has his own level that only he can see. Players must find a way to unlock and get to their exit door.<br> <br>To achieve this, you must cooperate by exchanging objects and trigger mechanisms that can affect both your side and your partner’s.<br><br>You'll need to communicate efficiently with your friend to beat all levels...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/600_150_C_11.png?t=1655243984\" /></span><br><br>Palallel has one specificity: <strong> You won’t be able to see or interact with your friend </strong><br><br>Communication is key to progress in parallel with your partner… Will you be able to solve puzzles while cooperating effectively ?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/600_150_C_12.png?t=1655243984\" /></span><br><br>To exchange an object, it’s simple: get it out of your board...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/ffee43394e4becb760b350d931d4555c.poster.avif?t=1655243984\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/ffee43394e4becb760b350d931d4555c.webm?t=1655243984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/ffee43394e4becb760b350d931d4555c.mp4?t=1655243984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>… and it will pop on the other, on the opposite side !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/600_150_C_13.png?t=1655243984\" /></span><br><br>Interact with buttons, switches, pressure plates and more to open the path to your friend.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/8e0f2437f6033a8bc8da7ae78520a972.poster.avif?t=1655243984\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/8e0f2437f6033a8bc8da7ae78520a972.webm?t=1655243984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/8e0f2437f6033a8bc8da7ae78520a972.mp4?t=1655243984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/600_150_C_14.png?t=1655243984\" /></span><br><br>You like physic-based games ? So do we !<br><br>Throw balls &amp; keys, use crates as a platform, play with gravity, … <br><br>Even in these boards, laws of physics still exist !.. Most of the time... Approximately…<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/1cdded180286b066b96471f5d3b0582b.poster.avif?t=1655243984\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/1cdded180286b066b96471f5d3b0582b.webm?t=1655243984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/1cdded180286b066b96471f5d3b0582b.mp4?t=1655243984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/600_150_C_15.png?t=1655243984\" /></span><br><br>When you reach the limit of a world, you'll encounter an &quot;END&quot; level, aka trial levels.<br><br>These levels are a bit different in the layout (not a single screen) and will be quite challenging.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/14819352cf51ebba58148a577429bf85.poster.avif?t=1655243984\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/14819352cf51ebba58148a577429bf85.webm?t=1655243984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/14819352cf51ebba58148a577429bf85.mp4?t=1655243984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/600_150_C_16.png?t=1655243984\" /></span><br><br>Customize your character as you want with multiple character parts to switch from.<br><br>Try out the randomize button to get impressive results real fast.<br><br>You can't see your partner but who said you couldn't be pretty to solve puzzle ?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/da57ebdcb4f5e2a699cb7c4c70c0ef65.poster.avif?t=1655243984\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/da57ebdcb4f5e2a699cb7c4c70c0ef65.webm?t=1655243984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/da57ebdcb4f5e2a699cb7c4c70c0ef65.mp4?t=1655243984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766860/extras/600_150_C_17.png?t=1655243984\" /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 144 Levels individual levels (among these : <strong>8</strong> trials levels, <strong>8</strong> logic rooms and <strong>32</strong> bonus challenges)<br></li><li> 36 Achievements to unlock !<br></li><li> 10 Themed environments<br></li><li> Several mechanics and interactive objects to challenge your brain and dexterity<br></li><li> <strong>Some </strong> easter eggs…<br></li><li> Character customization pushed to the limit</li></ul>",
